<exercise checkit-seed="0009" checkit-slug="P5" checkit-title="Expected Value">
    <statement>
        
                <p>
                    A resturant offers a grab bag of 14 fortune cookies, 4 of them have a discount of \$5 in them, 4 of them have a \$1 discount, and the rest have merely fortunes in them. If Kurbika grabs one at random, what is the expected value of the draw?
                </p> 
    </statement>
    <answer>
        <p>
            The expected value is <me>\frac{4}{14}(5) + \frac{4}{14}(1) + 0 = $1.71</me>
        </p>
    </answer>
</exercise>
